data.description: *** Aledo ISD! *** Morningstar Neighborhood! *** UNDER $400,000! You have to see your gorgeous new home in Morningstar neighborhood, in the heart of Bearcat Country! Your beautiful new home features, 3bed, 2bath with a flex space on an oversized, corner lot! The home is immaculately maintained & priced competitively to move quick. You'll be at home in this stunning, gourmet kitchen equipped with a large eat-in island, rolling granite & a large stainless steel sink. This stunning kitchen boasts of custom cabinetry & large built-in gas stovetop. Built-in buffet, coffee bar to make mornings even better. Open floorplan flows from kitchen into the living room and large dining area. The living room has a gorgeous corner, fireplace and generously sized, perfect space for cozy nights! Large homeowners’ suite is spacious with a large closet & laundry room access. Another added upgrade! & The back patio is a large & plumbed with gas.
